  "title": "A red star like UFO sighted by four people in Assis Chateaubriand-PR [1999]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/17/a-red-star-like-ufo-sighted-by-four-people-in-assis-chateaubriand-pr-1999/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-uJ",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>APRIL 21st, 1999</strong>. Time: 20h00 pm. Duration: 01h30m. In the city of Assis Chateaubriand, State of Paraná, on a night of clear sky and good visibility, four people spotted an unidentified flying object moving from the South to the North of the region. The UFO had a star shape and emitted an intermittent red light. Despite the good visibility condition for the sighting, the witnesses did not report seeing any condensation trail left by the observed object.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.546. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre a ocorrência de objeto voador não identificado na região do município de Assis Chateaubriand, Paraná”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
  "excerpt": "<p>APRIL 21st, 1999. Time: 20h00 pm. Duration: 01h30m. In the city of Assis Chateaubriand, State of Paraná, on a night of clear sky and good visibility, four people spotted an unidentified flying object moving from the South to the North of the region. The UFO had a star shape and emitted an intermittent red light. [&hellip;]</p>\n",
